description: This file serves as the development entry point for a Qwik application, responsible for client-side rendering without server-side rendering (SSR). It imports rendering functions from Qwik, a Root component, and exports a default function that initiates rendering into the document.

methods.name: default function
methods.description: Entry point function that invokes Qwik's render method to mount the Root component onto the document, using provided options.
